          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                ".The accuracy of the measured data was tested by",
                " measuring the n,p-scattering cross section under the",
                " same conditions.",
                ".Optical model calculations of the cross sections was",
